A towering crane in NYC toppled, crashing into apartment buildings, killing four and injuring many.
The crane split into pieces, demolishing multiple structures.
The tragic collapse occurred during construction, causing chaos and destruction.
Rescue crews worked tirelessly to find survivors in the rubble.
The incident highlighted the dangers of construction in the city.
Despite previous safety concerns, the crane's collapse shocked residents.
The aftermath saw a massive cleanup effort and questions about crane safety in NYC.
The tragic event added to a series of construction accidents in the city.
